<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔
				颜色;字型大小;段落1,颜色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落设定之间使用" , "分隔
				
				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				范例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符号，WILD会出现在每条转轮中。
					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>WIN</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>WILD can substitutes for any\nsymbol except BONUS\nSYMBOL and SCATTER\nSYMBOL.\n\nWIDL appears in 2,3,4 and\n5 reels.</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;SCATTER</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;18;AMOUNT  </TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;18;Payoff Odds  </TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;FREE GAME</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>Collect SCATTER SYMBOL\non reel 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 \nto trigger FREE GAME.</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>အႏိုင္ရသည့္အထိလွည့္ပါ</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT> မျောက်ကျွတ်ဝုခုန်း ဆနှုန်းမြင့်ဆုလဒ်ရ</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->
	</dict>
</plist>
